Employee Tracking Module (New)
Employee Side (Mobile App)
Face verification check-in / check-out powered by AI
Mark attendance with selfie + GPS location
Live location sharing (background tracking while on duty)
Start / Stop work session
View own attendance history
View total distance traveled per day/week/month
Manager Side (Web + Mobile)
Live map showing all active employees in real time
Employee location history playback (route replay on map)
Total travel distance per employee with timeline
Attendance records — present / absent / late / half-day
Face verification logs with photo evidence
Geofence alerts — notify when employee leaves assigned zone
Employee work session reports (check-in time, check-out time, duration)
Export attendance & travel reports (PDF / CSV)
Additional Features
Leave management — apply, approve, reject
Task assignment to field employees with location tagging
Beat/route planning — assign daily visit routes to employees
Customer visit tracking — log which customer was visited, when, and where
Salary & payroll summary based on attendance
Notifications — late check-in alerts, missed check-out reminders